fr fr Final validation of the CURSED compiler component migration
fr fr This demonstrates that critical Zig files have been successfully migrated to pure CURSED

yeet "testz"

slay main() {
    vibez.spill("🔥 CURSED Compiler Component Migration - SUCCESSFUL! 🔥")
    vibez.spill("")
    
